<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN355">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>matilu ñāyi liṉṟē kiṭaṅku</l>
<l>nīi riṉmaiyiṟ kaṉṟumēyn tukaḷu</l>
<l>mūratu nilaimaiyu mituvē.</l>
<l>(cu)vicumpu nītta miṟanta ñāyiṟṟup</l>
<l>pacuṅkatir civantu vāṅkantic ciṟunaṉi</l>
<l>piṟanta piṉṟaic ceṟipiṉac citāar</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The wall is without bastions, and the state of the village,</l>
<l>where, in the absence of water in the moat, the calves</l>
<l>graze [and] frolic, is this.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
